item.title: Reze cosplay (Chainsaw Man)
item.description: Ever since I went to see the movie back in November, I knew I had to cosplay her! It's a rather casual/closet cosplay - except for the top because I made it myself. I wanted to keep it rather "loose" (just like in the references I found of her), so it ended up having a bit of sheerness. Unfortunately, this kind of fabric is either opaque (but way too stiff for this kind of tailoring) or a bit sheer, so I chose the latter! *other socials: reddit: https://reddit.com/u/anna_himejima IG: https://instagram.com/anna_himejima

item.title: I kept wondering why she is alive.
item.description: I have no opinion about whether or not Epstein killed himself other than being a skeptic and Occam's razor... And there's a few things I get hung up on but why is she still alive? She knows as much if not more. She's angling for a pardon, and part of that is she might be signaling she's ready to release names. So now she's either a massive liability that is going to end up accidentally killed in jail. Are there windows to fall out of? But if the rest of the world has started their own serious investigations, especially Poland looking at ties to Russian intelligence... No matter how lawless and corrupt this administration is this global criminal conspiracy is going to end up knocking on our door. The release of those files had what I believe purposely shitty redaction from long-term DOJ people that have their hands tied. I think it's an act of rebellion how bad those redactions are. Those files painted enough of a global conspiracy that people can piece it together. It's happening, it's gaining momentum, I'VE NEVER WANTED ACCOUNTABILITY FOR SCUMBAGS MORE IN MY LIFE.
